    @startuml
    title Delegated Identity and Token Exchange
    skinparam backgroundColor transparent
    skinparam shadowing false
    skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
    skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

participant "User Token" as U
participant "Orchestration Token" as O
participant "Gateway Token" as G
participant "Executor Token" as E
participant "Tool Token" as T
participant "Resource Token" as R

U -> O : exchange / down-scope
O -> G : exchange / down-scope
G -> E : exchange / down-scope
E -> T : exchange / down-scope
T -> R : exchange / down-scope
note over U,R
Each token is short-lived, audience-restricted,
and linked to a policy decision identifier.
end note

    @enduml
